bio:
If you need to export Mercedes-Benz, VW, Seat, Skoda, Audi and Porshe data: like models, engines, partnumbers, pictures etc from ETKA or EPC catalogue - We can propose utilities for software database conversion to MySQL and others formats. 

What we provide:

 1. Database ETKA VW, Seat, Skoda, Audi in MySQL format: All information from the database, exploded diagrams, models, engines, partnumbers, images and other information;

 2. MERCEDES BENZ EWA net EPC database: All information from the database, exploded diagrams, models, engines, partnumbers, images and other information converted to MySQL format;

 3. Software for database conversion: parcers from original Electronic Parts Catalog for ETKA and EPCnet;

 4. Consulting services and support of our products: integration, SQL Query Builder, parcing from another databases, etc..

ETKA details genuine original parts from Volkswagen Group's four mainstream marques of automobiles, Volkswagen, SEAT, ¿koda, and Audi. It also covers Volkswagen Commercial Vehicles, Volkswagen Marine, and Volkswagen Industrial Motor. The coverage ranges from the 1947 Volkswagen Beetle, right through to the latest present day vehicles and associated applications.

EPCnet is a browser-based Electronic Parts Catalog which allows the user to specify virtually every spare part for the models covered. An intuitive graphical user interface permits easy navigation through the extensive parts catalog. Tutorials are available at no charge to help familiarize both new and experienced users with the Mercedes-Benz spare parts group system and the selection
